summit China Lake pump. Have the China Lake as your secondary. This gun is unique as it does an animation for every time you pull it out. Pull this out before you do your trickshot and then switch back to do the animation. Pistol swap. Have a pistol, preferably the Python or ASP. Simply pull it out, shoot it, and then switch back. Moni nac. Have a stakeout then press shoot, switch weapon, reload. Reload nac. Press triangle/y just before the clip goes into gun. (different timings) Tac insert cancel. Pull out your tactical insertion, start to use it and then cancel, switching to your primary. Dive stall. Silent shot with your weapon, then switch weapons 3 times in rapid succession. Immediately afterword dolphin dive while holding the shoot button, and your gun should be stuck in the diving animation Modern Warfare 3 Create a class. Either use the L8A1 or the MSR with impact and either heartbeat or extended magazines on them. You want Dead Silence Pro so you don't take damage when falling and Sleight of Hand Pro to switch weapons faster. Follow step 2 from Modern Warfare 2. Some of the better maps are
